snippet.title: MLB Power Pros (Wii) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of the Nintendo Wii version of MLB Power Pros, a 2007 baseball video game by Konami. The Arizona Diamondbacks face the home Los Angeles Dodgers. Using the Expert gameplay mode, so some of the normal UI elements are intentionally missing like the pitch aim and fly ball shadows.
